On the path of unfoldment, there's a magical space of confusion and uncertainty.

In the liminal space between crisis and a new state of being, we struggle with the loss of the old identity, while lacking a new one. We remain in a no-man's-land, without any clear sense of direction.

This space of uncertainty can be terrifying and exciting, but with discipline and devotion to the process, a profound transmutation can occur. 

Remaining in the uncertainty requires courage and faith, and asks that we refrain from rearranging our dismembered pieces back into the old ways. 

Our old parts project fearful future narratives, in the hopes of getting us to react and flee the purifying process.

Despite the pain and limitation that the old patterns may have caused, there's a familiarity in the chrysalis of the past; it feels safe. Here courage and faith in the process need to be activated.

One is asked to expand and hold a container for the process from a more mature place, where the struggle of the old parts can be observed, cared for, and parented. 

Repeatedly, the old patterns manage to capture our consciousness, get us to identify with their pain and struggle, to fuse us with the stories of the old.  But, we continue to increase our capacity to feel all that they bring, no matter how painful and unfamiliar, while expanding into a higher state of compassionate observation. 

In the process of holding the old parts, we grow our essence, we reveal the Self. The pain and sorrow of the dying old ways, become food for the emergence of the new. 

The old can be honoured and appreciated, because it had a purpose at that stage of development. 

Can I allow the old ways, things, and people to dissolve from my field; dissolve and leave the system, as my being integrates the lessons and calibrates to a higher level? Can I allow for a system open to a new set of experiences and possibilities, hitherto unavailable, to emerge?

How can I midwife this transmutation with care, discernment, patience, devotion, trust, and wisdom? The process asks that these faculties be activated and fine-tuned, lest it devour us, or worse – keep us in the prison of the old 🖤💛❤

Among a number of luminous conversations my dear friend Peter Limberg (The Stoa) and I had with some great people in Montreal this past weekend, the following nugget inspired me to share. From Peter: 

"Hurt people, hurt people. The inverse is also true, as my friend Nicolas Benjamin said to us yesterday in a moment of channelled inspiration: “healed people heal people.” The resonance I had with this lovely phrase is threefold: 1) my healing journey is not in service for myself, but for those I live for, 2) finding the wise asymmetry in social dynamics is the right orientation, aka in certain ways I am more healed than others, and others are more healed than me, 3) create a culture that focuses on phrases that spiral you towards the whole, rather than phrases that accurately describe why we are not."

The extent of crimes against children is shocking and unimaginable. 

A heavy and tragic price has been paid by those courageous enough to sound the alarm. 

Signs of these horrors have been around us for a while, yet general incredulity at their scale and extent has kept the majority of us from even considering their reality. 

Empire has held much power over its puppets through the blackmail economy, especially through the use of innocent souls. 

But the contracts of silence are crumbling. The leash is being loosened. More light shines into darkness.  

Whether it's the island, the fashion industry, or the many hundreds of other institutions and instances that many of us have been aware of -- it will be revealed. It's time. 

In regards to this, I'd like to share a hypothesis that I believe holds truth:

In times past, as our collective inner children were banished to the depths of our repressed psyches, reality mirrored this in the real world with the wholescale exploitation and abuse of the legions of forgotten children. 

But now, as more of us rescue our inner-children from the caverns of our inner world, re-parenting, loving, and integrating them into our being – we see reality mirror this by releasing and revealing the many tormented and imprisoned little souls in the outer world. As we heal the inner, so we heal the outer. 

LOVE & COURAGE 👧🏾👦🧑🏾👩‍🦰🧒🏾👱‍♀️

A happy Winter Solstice to all friends in the Northern Hemisphere 🌌☀️

During the longest and darkest night of the year, the light returns and begins its expansive journey back to the apex of the Summer Solstice. Light and Dark, friend and foe. The cyclical beauty of duality creates, confounds, challenges, and teaches. 

I find a textured beauty in the sublime descent of light into the darkest crevices of creation. It carries flavours of both grief and triumph – and reminds me of the greater game.

Respect to all who've brought more light into their darkness this year. To all who've made friends with the barren inner lands, pulled the weeds, and seeded fresh new gardens. May you enjoy the fruits of your labour. The world certainly will. 

Whether we willingly descend into ourselves, or are nudged off the ledge through crisis – it's the willingness to take the journey that echoes throughout time and space. 

With every dip -- a sharper blade, a softer heart ❤

#wintersolstice

It is here.
"I and the Father are one."
❤

Empire crumbles in direct proportion to courageous action, coming from clear perception and love. 

The emerging strangeness of our realm, is a benevolent invitation to identify where we choose to remain attached to our puppet strings, and dissolve them. There is safety in being a puppet. But there is no dignity, adventure, or ecstasy.  

As Empire continues its clumsy attempt to colonize the minds, souls, and bodies of its subjects – many others are choosing the path of expansion, liberation, and wisdom. Good. There's no going back. 

The tragicomedy of the last three years has served as a portal of awakening for many. We've seen the consequences of a hostile herd mentality, and the blind trust in degenerate institutions. 

Sadly, we've seen what some of our fellow humans are capable of when they're not in touch with the wisdom of their bodies, the clarity of their minds, or the light of their souls. Unfortunately, we're also seeing the unfolding consequences of this.

If we don't face the guilt, shame, and fear inside of us – these things will make us buckle to the collective madness. Guilt, shame, and fear are the universal tools of Empire. The individual – centred – remains determined and unswayed, grounded in truth. This is the gift of facing one's most nausea-inducing inner parts, and coming out a stud. 

Despite the cunning campaign of hostility and division, many of us learned more compassion, more understanding, and more self-sufficiency. We clarified the kind of life we want, and the kind of life we're done with – forever. ⚔❤

In collaboration with the wonderful Jenn Mansell @jlmansell -- inspired by her reflections in one of our conversations.

At the back of the heart, there is a door that opens with each visit of excruciating pain and heartbreak. Ancient grief flows out, and does not stop. All past loss and disappointment – ready to be expressed in a moment if we can simply hold it and allow it. With time, our capacity increases to stay with the waves and let them integrate. 

With every shatter of the heart, the door lets out some more. Every heartbreak is a link to every prior one – all the way back to the beginning. Life cracks the heart, the door flings open. An opportunity arises to clear, liberate, and renew. 

This terrifying moment is an invitation; to feel and to heal– all that's been buried and denied. 

The darkness fully seen, turns into light – the grief compassionately embraced, turns into love. Each crack is where the light comes in, each crack is where the pain gets out.

The pain and love are intertwined by the distorted perceptions of past hurts. Aliveness and vitality follow the release and integration of all the pain that's been trapped inside for so long. 

In this open space the heart remembers; wholeness.
❤🖤💛

I feel inspired to offer a brief period of free calls at this time, to anyone who's interested in entering a dialogue with an openness to seeing what emerges. The intention is to discover what's alive, pertinent, and useful on our journey of expansion. 🌟

1 on 1 -- 30 min Calls, February 20 – March 17

Link in bio to book a call 🌄

Spring is here for the people of the northern hemisphere. 🌳

As the astounding force of nature moves through our world with her raw power and grace, we can use her guidance to propel ourselves into renewal and vitality. 

We can align ourselves to the cyclical rebirth by opening, blooming, and using the ample birthing energy for profound expansion. More life, more beauty. 

There's an invitation to move toward a new personal and collective vision by choosing to be IN-SPIRED.

Life sweeps through its creations, and invites all to rise once again into fresh glory; to grow, to play, to shine – to radiate the simple dignity of BEING.  

Inner and outer structures that once had a function, are now ready to be shaken off so that more life and vitality can emerge. The old must collapse, so that the new may be born. This is the process, this is the way. 

We're in it. 

Just as a seed must grow through the hull that once held it, but now limits it – so must the stagnant old structures, habits, and beliefs fall off, so that more harmonized ones can emerge. 

As the lifeless patterns fall away and our disoriented parts despair, we can look to nature and remember the cycles of death and rebirth that are the foundational code of our manifest experience on this mysterious plane. 

Through the fresh VISION we seed into our lives, we awaken constellations of probable realities, and birth them through our actions – through our thoughts, words, and deeds. 

Nature blooms in ever greater wonder, with awesome power and profound grace – modelling the potential of our own creative powers.

If we align to the greater natural rhythm and allow to be IN-SPIRED, we can shape what comes through, and trust that we can open ever wider to allow for beauty, connection, and creativity to emerge. 

Every season has a song, and with each change we sing along 😉⚔❤

Heretics who weave the Golden Chain, are you coming to remember all the lifetimes? 

All of time leads to the one final and inevitable moment; the removal of our earthly cloak, to reveal the truth of I and I.

He & Her, Inner & Outer – dancing, weaving, acting out the drama. Victim, villain – mapping out all possible experience.   

Moving through the underworld of our personal and collective souls, purifying the artifacts of ancient genetic lineages – at last to meet each other with a clear sight.

Here now, reality continues to collapse, as an invitation and a push; to know ourselves. All illusions crumble so that only what is true remains. 

As it is written – as it has been foretold;
In the end, all burns away – except the light of Love, the essence of the ONE

❤⚔

*Music by the legendary Ulf Söderberg, “Tempel Och Katedral Reser Sig Ur Djupen”

I'm impressed by Nicolas Canon's @nicocanon_ wisdom regarding sacred relationships. I'd like to learn more, and I'd like to invite you to join us for a live call at The Stoa, on Tuesday, May 30th at 12:00 EST, with a Q & A at the end. The conversation will be available on YouTube after. 

☀️ We find ourselves in a time of fracture, dissolution, and renewal. As we undergo a collective reorganization of values, meaning, and purpose – we discover one of the foundational elements of a healthy society; the sanctity of a romantic relationship. 

The disaster of modern dating and noncommittal transactional relationships has created a profound need for deeper connection with an other. 

A conscious relationship is the alchemical container of mutual soul development, in service of unconditional love. As we move through our shadow projections and wounded parts, we discover a truer sense of self, and touch a more real experience with the other.  

How can men respond to the call for greater devotion to creating, nourishing, and sustaining a conscious relationship? What is the role of the emerging sacred masculine in holding the container for depth, truth, and love? Let us inquire. ☀️

By fully occupying our body and this present moment experience, we align with the razor's edge of creation as it occurs. What used to be an automatic emergence of our preconceptions that paint the world with meaning -- now becomes a creative choice. 

Every numb and forgotten part of our bodies is reclaimed – millimetre by cubic millimetre – by the warm light of our loving awareness. This awareness frees, little by little, every prisoner from the dungeons of our past – the anguish and torment, now serving as the fertilizer of our soul. 

With a conscious embodiment of our form, we animate a new story of our choosing, free from the chains of the past. As the chains try to bind us yet again out of habit, we CHOOSE the felt sense of the body – here now – and dance into creation. Thus, free-will emerges, one free choice at a time. 

Those of us who do not wish to look within and free our past -- end up projecting our pain and create darkness in the world. Those who look within and take responsibility for their transformation -- dissolve the collective darkness, and bring in more Goodness – by word, thought, and deed. 

In the face of our collective madness, there is a network of ever-more aligned and calibrated humans, who are striving for integrity on all fronts. ⚡They hold the signal through their bodies, for the realignment of all⚡
   
Juicy work 🔥🌹💦

Imagine being so out of touch with reality that when challenged with reason and facts, your only refuge is to paint hard data which concerns the well-being and expansion of humanity, as a “conspiruuuhcee theory”.

Imagine having no capacity to entertain anything other than pre-digested, low-risk/high-reward opinions, sanctioned and rewarded by Empire.

Imagine betraying the truth in your heart and the dignity of your being, in order to parrot lies in exchange for cheap prestige and wealth. 

Then, imagine all of the institutions that shielded you, and which seemed so indestructible, begin to crumble. No longer able to reward or protect you from your delusion, in the face of truth.

Imagine being exposed as a hack publicly, and worse still – being exposed for wilfully abusing your position as an “authority” to deceive and harm large numbers of people. 

Many such cases, and many more to come. It's a time of R-E-V-E-A-L-I-N-G

🙃🥳🤥

At the time of making the film, I knew that the four shots pointing to these horrors would not be understood by many – yet. 

But, my sense was that as we stepped deeper into the period of revelation, more of the dark tapestry would be undone – thread by thread – illuminating what once seemed like an eccentric fantasy.  

The main point that needs to be understood as we enter greater confusion and turbulence, is that these horrors are occurring at the highest places of our culture, perpetrated by humans in prominence.

It needs to be understood that these horrors are institutionalized, and are part of the daily transactions of the managerial class, as a necessary part of their deranged ecosystem.

There are levels to the game. In very simple terms:

1. Mundane:
Traumatized humans unwilling or unable to process their pain, perpetuate the same horrors onto the next generations. Here we have a combination of personal trauma complexes, and perhaps, discarnate entity attachments.

Fact check ✔ 

2. Parapolitical:
Horrors perpetrated as part of blackmailing operations of politicians, celebrities, leaders of industry, etc. Also done as “team-building”, assurance of loyalty, synchronized opinions/messaging, etc. This is an indispensable piece in the arsenal of centralized global governance.

Fact check ✔ 

3. Transpersonal:
Rituals with the purpose of siphoning pure light into the super-sensible realms, to sustain the trapped....

Fact check ✔ 

Deep breath -------------------------------------- and exhale.

This issue is a linchpin in the collective delusion we are awakening from. My encouragement, if you have the stomach for it, is to shine more light on it with persistence and artful communication. Recognizing the reality of these horrors takes time, as it triggers much dormant trauma within all of us. When grounded in ourselves, we can be kind and patient with all. 

It is happening ⚔❤
@ourrescue

The choice to bond deeply with another is a revolutionary act ⚔❤

To braid two stories into one.

Aligned with clarity – within a vision – a shared mission. 

To claim and own each other – fully.

With pride aside, humility awakens – the ego freed from its imperative to separate. 

🌹Acceptance + Curiosity + Appreciation🌹

ACCEPTANCE – opens the field, neutralizes the ego
CURIOSITY – feels into the other, inviting their essence in
APPRECIATION – savours that essence, gifting the other the reflection of its beauty

Empire wants single units – atomized, disposable, insatiable.

Shallow transactions – masks impressing masks.

No acceptance, no curiosity, no appreciation.

With each touch – to take, to steal. 

Giving over to the lowest bidder – freely, cheaply. 

Fortified, unhurt, unloved. 

BUT – firmly nested and held by the mystery;

1 + 1 alchemize their fragments in the container of this Now.

Renewing the vow – moment to moment – with courage + commitment. 
In the presence of it ALL.

⚡

This year: 

Do we shrink and accept the unimaginative story of:
Impoverishment, war, fear, constriction, cowardice, strife, and obedience.

OR – 

Do we rise and expand into the VISION of:
Beauty, creativity, eros, creation, courage, and thumos.

A choice.

Accepting the mainstream story of reality robs one of their personal spark. One becomes a consenting passenger on a train to nowhere. It requires no vitality or creativity, just a lifeless slide into oblivion. 

Holding a VISION requires presence, vitality, and lucidity. It inspires one to be here now, basking in the glorious dance of life. 

Without a VISION, we dance to the lame tune of the ruling degenerate tricksters.

A VISION is a conscious creation. Accepting the dis-empowering stories fabricated by think-tanks, is an unconscious disavowal of personal power. 

VISION comes out of wakefulness and vitality.

Without activating the wakeful energy of our inherent aliveness, the momentum of our fictitious self recreates the same old low-energy patterns that keep us imprisoned in our dissatisfied smallness.

A VISION is maintained by will, yet kept open to Divine Inspiration.

To hold a noble VISION is to act as a conduit for God's will -- to be a harmonizing rod.

Holding a VISION requires one to be fully in their body, to be firmly planted on this Earth, and to be permeated by the Supernal – to know that one belongs to this here now, and from here, to broadcast the signal of the VISION with gentle power, radiant with the glory of creation. 

The VISION creates a field of inspiration, intuition, and aligned action. 

As we hold the VISION, its field begins to inform our reality, and infuses our activities and inspiration with its essence. 

The VISION begins to manifest.

Bringing down, holding, and invoking a greater VISION, is a heroic, non-egoic act. 

Seeking purpose? Hold a VISION greater than any that's ever been enacted on this Earth -- then move toward it. And when the ego tries to make you feel ridiculous for doing so, expand wider and hold the VISION even more boldly. 

Or shrink.

A choice 
👁⚔❤
